{"tid":1435850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃藍絲攬炒] 一齊估下北角樓價會點跌法 (附元朗樓市新聞)","createTime":"2019-08-09T07:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:39:14.000Z","uid":187489,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"040928c96b745dbd43fca0ec1a8ad1a7b3d1065d","tid":1435850,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"呢個post唔講光復、唔講警察、唔講政府，只講樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lJoCdBCjvOI/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlJoCdBCjvOI%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=0e2d5814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n福建叔叔：北角我黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (設計對白)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hA2rTM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhA2rTM7.jpg&h=0beeed16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位東區市民，經過元朗一役，唔理你咩立場，都應該睇到<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">當日俾黑社會斬嘅，其實中年人仲多過後生仔。</span></strong>希望大家可以諗下將來每晚收工或者出街會有幾人心惶惶、諗下<strong>當北角變成第2個元朗，治安一去不返</strong>，自己嗰區嘅樓價一沉不起，仲返唔返到轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=4]<span style=\"color: gold;\">今天不出來<br />\n明天出不來</span>[/size=5]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7272/7486786114_05e63dc5eb_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7272%2F7486786114_05e63dc5eb_b.jpg&h=ee62a91e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位北角友，東區友，<br />\n我唔求你地衝、唔求你地遊行，<br />\n只望你地下次附近有事發生時願意落去聲援，<span style=\"color: gold;\">令屋企無辜家人唔好吸到過期山埃</span>。<br />\n<br />\n自己家園自己救。<br />\n<br />\n今日新聞：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2019年8月9日<br />\n【逃犯條例】過期催淚彈或釋出山埃氣體學者：濃度高可致命｜香港01｜政情</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190809/mobile/bkn-20190809110255601-0809_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190809%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190809110255601-0809_00822_001.html&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=7a322b6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190809/mobile/bkn-20190809110255601-0809_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>吸入催淚氣體後遺症嚴重或致命　公院醫生斥警方濫用化武</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2422962/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%90%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E6%B0%A3%E9%AB%94%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%BA%E7%97%87%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E3%80%80%E5%85%AC%E9%99%A2%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%BF%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%8C%96%E6%AD%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2422962%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%2581%25BA%25E7%2597%2587%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2591%25BD%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258C%2596%25E6%25AD%25A6&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=7cc44d18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2422962/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%90%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E6%B0%A3%E9%AB%94%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%BA%E7%97%87%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E3%80%80%E5%85%AC%E9%99%A2%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%BF%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%8C%96%E6%AD%A6</a></span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎轉貼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qVJe.88nN3dNwajDmEW_Lw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU4/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-08/6e04b6e0-ba55-11e9-bfbf-9090b23ec883\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FqVJe.88nN3dNwajDmEW_Lw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-08%2F6e04b6e0-ba55-11e9-bfbf-9090b23ec883&h=98f657b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"054448fdb11bd7e5afbf7eb24d6917b27425a743","tid":1435850,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:15:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3bef0fae0845e206d2845cc3b10a36821388513","tid":1435850,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"北角冇架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3e8f8bb5ac35dd46e1f24b7a4cb8696e43b646","tid":1435850,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">自己家園自己救</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b9ae191d5f5ebc6d7de80830edd2309d5a283e80","tid":1435850,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"推 我唔要有第2個元朗"},{"pid":"babf46062031c5c9d8e74689f52a6f60c484696e","tid":1435850,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:23:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b97b3ac0d6485bb93c003dbef7c3facb90c84486","tid":1435850,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"出發！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"3eaee836469bb5fdf41a147468c7932eb913edeb","tid":1435850,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMJqUur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMJqUur.jpg&h=36fb98e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，成為過街老鼠，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=1722809e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">46,460</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 12:55）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"e4e1ee9806ef176c94648c0ca1cc7bf051cce964","tid":1435850,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"恭喜晒東區嘅居民 你地成功令自己層樓冇得升了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}